
iROCs goal is to help Support Groups support individuals with life and learning challenges, as well as those with ADHD and Executive Functioning difficulties become more Independent, Responsible, Organized, and Confident through practical everydaysolutions.

iROCs Academic Coaching (specialized tutoring):  iROC has indepth knowledge and expertise in working with K8 students that have learning challenges, as well as those that are diagnosed with ADHD, Learning Disabilities, High Functioning Autism, identified as Gifted and Talented, emtotionally disturbed, and have executive functioning and/or social skill difficulties.

iROCs ADHD / Executive Functioning (ADHD/EF) Coaching: customized to fit individuals academic, professional, and personal/parenting goals, as well as their specific life styles to maximize their individual growth potentials.

